('19950300115', '199503001', 15, 'img;The diagram shows a quadrilateral ABCD where A is (6, 1), B is on the x-axis and C is (1, 3). ;The diagonal BD bisects AC at right angles at M and BD = 3.5 BM. Find;(a)	the equation of BD,;(b)	the x-coordinate of B,;(c)	the coordinate of D,;(d)	the area of the quadrilateral ABCD.;By considering the area of triangle ABD, or otherwise, find the perpendicular distance from D to BA extended.', 'Exam', 46, 4601, 4, NULL, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
